{"tid":2396515,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"水炮車射有線記者 投訴警察課事隔一年多回覆：警員無過錯 已作適當訓示","createTime":"2021-02-05T15:49:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T02:29:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"2afe6c61f3c36c5ef38397b998053cec6522c165","tid":2396515,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:49:43.000Z","msg":"反送中運動期間，警方多次被質疑縱容前線防暴警員濫用武力，記協亦曾發聲明，強烈譴責警方無理襲擊記者。有線新聞台一名記者早前向警方投訴，指2019年9月採訪示威期間，被警方水炮車噴中催淚水。事隔一年多，投訴警察課回覆結果，裁定警員無過錯。<br />\n<br />\n警方於2019年拒絕民陣於9月15日就「國際民主日」的遊行和集會申請，惟當日有網民自發到港島上街，警方出動水炮台驅散人群。<br />\n<br />\n《有線新聞》指，該台記者當日在中環添華道採訪期間，被警方水炮車噴中藍色催淚水劑，其後投訴警方濫用職權。報道引述投訴警察課回覆指，調查顯示，當時環境混亂，多人佔路及暴力衝擊警方防線，使用催淚水劑驅散符合警方程序及法律條文，故把指控列為「並無過錯」。警方指，已把事件通知有關人員，並作出適當訓示。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/KJUEOPY5FBHELFOMJJPW5QBMDY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FKJUEOPY5FBHELFOMJJPW5QBMDY%2F&d=07E5ZYF2Wb2hLaoCEA3MjDpVG5rzq85IoANuBgA9bzA%3D&h=ff41ea87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210205%2FKJUEOPY5FBHELFOMJJPW5QBMDY%2F&h=fdc46c80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210205/KJUEOPY5FBHELFOMJJPW5QBMDY/</a>"},{"pid":"b1d3bfc1650e56dd7734d3d2f5f568346f8d89a8","tid":2396515,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55af19cca1f6827b8fb075f33c32e493e6a84dc7","tid":2396515,"uid":291750,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:51:41.000Z","msg":"黑警有咩會做錯呀！"},{"pid":"f29118eaf6db89eb9441c783739fef779421092e","tid":2396515,"uid":389613,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:51:56.000Z","msg":"響香港做香港人同元朝做漢人